name: Custom fabric and burlap banner 4 feet wedding decor rustic wedding banner rustic baby shower decor
description:
My custom made fabric banners add delight to any wedding, event, bridal shower, baby shower, photo prop/backdrop, nursery, child's bedroom, or just as a whimsical decoration in your home. Our fabric banners are full of fabric that I find at local thrift stores, goodwill, yard sales etc..I dye some of them to match whatever color you like! 

This listing is for a 4 foot banner. 

I will work with you to get the perfect color for your theme! The one in the first photo was a custom one for a wedding shower and the theme was tiffany blue, white and burlap...

i AM OUT OF VINTAGE BURLAP SO I WOULD HAVE TO BUY THE BURLAP NEW. 

I have so many other colors and patterns to choose from...so if you want a pattern with solids please convo me so I can send photos if needed. 

This listing is for a 4 ft. banner. 
Color for banner (I like to use 3 to 5 colors) 
If you are not sure before you purchase send me a convo and we can work the color out...

IF YOU WANT LONGER BANNERS I CAN QUOTE PRICES....

Please allow 5-7 business days to make it and ship it....Thanks
